P_A(X)=\begin{vmatrix}3-X&0&-1 \\  2&4-X&2 \\  -1&0&3-X\end{vmatrix}&=(4-X)\begin{vmatrix}3-X&-1 \\ -1&3-X\end{vmatrix} \\ &=(4-X)(X^2-6X+8) \\ &=(4-X)(X-4)(X-2) \\ &=(2-X)(4-X)^2
